{
  "stem": "13833.2",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "After Raoul got 350 people helping, Christians and Jews, because, you know, Budapest is a very small city.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And it went like a wildfire that there is an angel who is helping.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And he came with a list of people, the Jewish organizations in Budapest whom he contacted.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And so they worked together.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And first, his idea was that he can take the Jews out of Budapest.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So he went to the top Hungarian Arrow Cross man.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And he offered them to take the Jews off their hand.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And he said--",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "This was-- well, he came in, in July.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And this was about the end of August.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And it's about the end of--",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--August--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Save Hungarians.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But in the meantime--",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--these 350 people also offered their apartments and their villas on the two side of the Danube to the Swedish Embassy.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And you will hear that all the time-- they're lying about it.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They said that he bought all those houses.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And he paid all the helpers.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He never bought any house because he thought he helps the Jews to keep those houses.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So they only made kiddings that the Swedish Embassy was the greatest landowners of Budapest.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Because the Swedish flag went out of the houses.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And we had a Christian or a Jewish boy who looked very Christian in Nazi uniform-- because many Nazis died already-- and taking care of our Swedish houses.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But it was still empty.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Not yet, no.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That's what he asked them, that I take them out.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I take them with a train through Germany into Sweden.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they said, fine, you can take 5,000 people.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Now, you probably always hear the people saying this is a passport.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "This is-- it is not.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
